paper_metadata.title: MAIN TEXT
paper_metadata.extraction_summary: Extracted BRCA2 variant information and penetrance data from a study on breast cancer patients.

patients.demographics: Unselected breast cancer patients, age range 25.1–79.9 years

functional_data.summary: Among the 42 BRCA2 carriers, there were 33 unique BRCA2 pathogenic variants (18 frameshift deletions, 3 frameshift insertions, 9 truncating and 3 splice sites).

variants.additional_notes: More than half of all BRCA2 carriers (24/42, 57.1%) had a pathogenic variant on exon 11.
key_quotes: Among the 42 BRCA2 carriers, there were 33 unique BRCA2 pathogenic variants (18 frameshift deletions, 3 frameshift insertions, 9 truncating and 3 splice sites).
Over half of all BRCA2 carriers (24/42, 57.1%) had a pathogenic variant on exon 11.

extraction_metadata.notes: Only BRCA2 variants were extracted as per instructions.
